\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Voice Acting Spreadsheet Connect launches the VASC web interface allowing users to import spreadsheet to make their Reaper session smarter.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The tool allows for Recording session preparation with a guide track that includes data from the spreadsheet, as well as metadata markers for embedding at export.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Multiple scripts are found in this repo to make Dialog recording more efficient and less prone to errors.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This tool wouldn't have been possible without following Aaron Cendan's work on UCS Renaming tool as a template. Thanks Aaron!\par}
}

